data.description: Welcome to your mountain sanctuary! This stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of natural beauty and modern comfort, boasting panoramic mountain views that will take your breath away. Step into the expansive living room, bathed in natural light streaming through numerous windows and a beautiful French door that showcase the awe-inspiring scenery surrounding this property. The focal point of the room is a beautiful fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance, making it the perfect space to unwind and enjoy the warmth of both the fire and the captivating views. The well-appointed kitchen, complete with modern appliances and ample counter space, is a haven for culinary enthusiasts. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing a family feast, the adjacent dining area provides the perfect setting to enjoy delicious meals while soaking in the mesmerizing mountain vistas. This home features three spacious bedrooms, each offering a peaceful retreat with views that will make waking up a delight. The finished basement adds versatility to the property, hosting a private bedroom and bathroom that can serve as a guest suite, home office, or a cozy den to escape and relax.  As you step outside, the expansive deck beckons you to take in the fresh mountain air and marvel at the breathtaking views that stretch across the horizon. Nestled among the trees, this property provides the perfect balance of serenity and privacy.  The two-car garage offers convenience for your vehicles and outdoor gear, ensuring that you can fully embrace the mountain lifestyle.  This home is a true haven for those seeking a retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. If you've been dreaming of a home with panoramic mountain views, a large living room with a fireplace, and a peaceful setting surrounded by nature, this is your opportunity.  Besides electronics and artwork, this home is 100% Turnkey.  With all the upgrades already completed, all it needs is you!
